| *Comment* | setup Account Logo test |  |
| set | logo_acc | logo-acc-%%start_time%% |
| set | logo_ws | logo-ws-%%start_time%% |
| set | logo_user | `logo-%%start_time%%@ken.socialtext.net` |

| st-admin | create-account --name %%logo_acc%% --title %%logo_acc%% | was created |
| st-admin | create-user --email %%logo_user%% --password %%password%% --account %%logo_acc%% | was created |
| st-admin | create-workspace --name %%logo_ws%% --title %%logo_ws%% --account %%logo_acc%% | was created |
| st-admin | add-member --email %%logo_user%% --workspace %%logo_ws%% | now has the role |
| st-admin | add-member --email %%logo_user%% --workspace %%workspace%% | now has the role |
| st-admin | add-member --email %%username%% --workspace %%logo_ws%% | now has the role |
| st-admin | give-accounts-admin --email %%logo_user%% | now has accounts admin access |
| st-admin | enable-plugin --plugin dashboard --account %%logo_acc%% |  |

| *Comment* | SEE: Login as %%logo_user%% |  |
| open_ok | /%%wiki%% |  |
| st-logoutin | %%logo_user%% | %%password%% |
| open_ok | /nlw/control/account |  |
| wait_for_element_visible_ok | link=%%logo_acc%% |  |
| click_ok | link=%%logo_acc%% |  |
| wait_for_element_visible_ok | link=Account Logo |  |
| click_ok | link=Account Logo |  |
